Entry.JapaneseText: ぼく思い出したよ…… いろいろ思い出しちゃった……
Entry.EnglishText: I remember now...I remember...a lot of things...

Entry.JapaneseText: 思い出したって…… 自分が精霊だったこと……？
Entry.EnglishText: Remember? You mean your life as a Summon Spirit...?

Entry.JapaneseText: うん……たくさん悪さした…… ……精霊の力で街壊したり……
Entry.EnglishText: Yes...I've done very bad things...I've destroyed...so many towns...

Entry.JapaneseText: みんなのことが嫌いだった。 ぼくの存在に気づかなくて すごく悲しかった……
Entry.EnglishText: I grew to hate everything. Everyone. I was so tired... My existence...it was one full of misery...

Entry.JapaneseText: ぼく、いけない子なんだ…… きみたちと一緒にいる 資格なんて……
Entry.EnglishText: I've made too many wrongs... I've sinned too much...Too much to be around with you two...

Entry.JapaneseText: そんなことないよ、エト！
誰でも、悪いことをしちゃう 可能性がある
Entry.EnglishText: Anyone has the potential to do wrong. We are all capable of sinning.

Entry.JapaneseText: 大切なのはその後、 それとどう向き合うか ってことなんじゃないかな
Entry.EnglishText: What's really important is what we do after! What we do to face our mistakes!

Entry.JapaneseText: ヤな思い出を受け入れるって 覚悟したから、エトの 記憶が戻ったんだろ？
Entry.EnglishText: If your memories are back that means you were sure you could handle the ugly truth, right?

Entry.JapaneseText: ぼくは…… ふたりのために……
そっか……ふたりがいたから、 ぼくはどんないやな思い出も 受け止められた……
Entry.EnglishText: I...decided that no matter how terrible the memories were... I couldn't bear to see you suffer...

Entry.JapaneseText: やっぱり……ぼくは…… <DIO>と<MEL>の 『お母さん』なんだ……
Entry.EnglishText: I guess...despite everything I'm still your mother, <DIO> and <MEL>...

Entry.JapaneseText: へん……エトなんて、 『お母さん』って感じ と違うくせに……
Entry.EnglishText: Weird...I don't quite see Eto as anything like a mother.

Entry.JapaneseText: でも……きみたちとの思い出が ぼくをぼくでいさせてくれたよ……
Entry.EnglishText: But...I still chose to remember... For you...

Entry.JapaneseText: 精霊のぼくじゃなくて、 きみたちと一緒に暮らしてきた ぼくで……
Entry.EnglishText: I'm no Summon Spirit...I want to live with you all my life.

Entry.JapaneseText: きみたちがいてくれてよかった…… きみたちの役に立てて……
Entry.EnglishText: Thank you for being here... Thank you for everything...You've done too much for me...

Entry.JapaneseText: ともかく、一旦、 家に戻って……
Entry.EnglishText: At any rate, let's hurry her back to the house...

Entry.JapaneseText: 罪を犯した者を…… 制裁するため
Entry.EnglishText: You who have committed a grave sin. It is well due time for retribution.

Entry.JapaneseText: たぶんこの『虹輪』のことです
Entry.EnglishText: By sin do you mean the Prism Ring?

Entry.JapaneseText: どけ、<RND>。 死にたくないのであれば
Entry.EnglishText: Move, <RND>. I do not want to kill you.

Entry.JapaneseText: <RND_P>さん…… ダオスとお知り合い、 なのですか……？
Entry.EnglishText: Rody... Could it be you and Dhaos are acquaintances...?

Entry.JapaneseText: なんせ、私にこの指輪を くれた人だもん
Entry.EnglishText: Of course, after all he's the one that gave me my ring...

Entry.JapaneseText: 退いて、ダオス…… 私はあなたが手を汚すのを……
Entry.EnglishText: Go away, Dhaos. You dirtying your hands with blood...
...is something I never want to see!!

Entry.JapaneseText: 意思が沿わぬならば 奴らともども おまえを消すまで
Entry.EnglishText: If that is your wish then run away. Otherwise I will crush you along these.

Entry.JapaneseText: 待てよ！ あんたは オレらの罪がどうとか 言ってっけど、
Entry.EnglishText: Hey wait a sec! You keep saying we committed a sin...

Entry.JapaneseText: オレらは まだそいつの後始末を してねーんだって
Entry.EnglishText: ...But we fixed everything in the end! It's all ok now!

Entry.JapaneseText: まだ、どうしてこんなことが 起きたかわかんないままだもん
Entry.EnglishText: I don't really understand why you hold such deep grudge to go all this way but...

Entry.JapaneseText: ちゃんとその罪と向き合って 何が悪かったのか、
Entry.EnglishText: ...If we face our sin with all our might, whatever it is, we can do nothing but good.

Entry.JapaneseText: それをわたしたちが どうすればいいのか、 ちゃんと答えを出したい
Entry.EnglishText: So please, just tell us what sort of sin is! We can work on it!

Entry.JapaneseText: もし<MEL>の魔法の使い方が 悪かったんなら、 それを改めなきゃだし
Entry.EnglishText: Sure, <MEL>'s magic may have created the Prism Ring. But it's all over now!

Entry.JapaneseText: オレのフォローが 悪かったんなら、なんか 考えなきゃいけない
Entry.EnglishText: She's never done anything evil as long as I've known her.

Entry.JapaneseText: だから、今、あんたに 『セイサイ』させられないんだ！
おまえたちの罪は 私が知っている
Entry.EnglishText: I know very well of the sin you committed.

Entry.JapaneseText: おまえたちが それを知ったとて、 再び罪を繰り返すだけ
Entry.EnglishText: If knowledge about said sin was disclosed I have no doubt you would simply repeat it all over again.

Entry.JapaneseText: だから、ここで おまえたちを消す。 向き合う必要はない
Entry.EnglishText: Thus, facing your sins is unnecessary...because I will erase you from existence!

Entry.JapaneseText: でも……わたしたちも ここでやられるわけには いかないよ
Entry.EnglishText: Even if that's so...We can't just give up after all we've been through!

Entry.JapaneseText: あいつは、私が…… 止める……！
